{"tid":1778550,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[推上熱門 ]點解熱門無行動POST？ 1212「齊上齊落」集會呀！","createTime":"2019-12-11T04:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T10:54:18.000Z","uid":42194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"85e6cecde3b7b81efd4c03d4533ef9e3bcd3984e","tid":1778550,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:54:23.000Z","msg":"手足唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />半年黎流過嘅汗、血、淚唔係白費<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">12/12「齊上齊落」集會 - 612半週年紀念</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤回暴動定性 撤銷義士控罪</span></strong></span><br />\n日期︰2019年12月12日(四)<br />\n時間︰19:00 - 21:00<br />\n地點︰愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦︰#民間集會團隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*已發出不反對通知書</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVAaXzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVAaXzV.jpg&h=0c440d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbXgS5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbXgS5f.jpg&h=2c97a1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnY0AiA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnY0AiA.jpg&h=421d1cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HqY6qf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HqY6qf.jpg&h=b5e87e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpPOKbW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpPOKbW.jpg&h=85b8a839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbzrvRW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbzrvRW.jpg&h=e9f45ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zud0AiB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZud0AiB.jpg&h=ee67e8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8tDmYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8tDmYC.jpg&h=03cea498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5oLNc5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5oLNc5.gif&h=806025d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思有D 文宣改唔切不反果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝文宣手足靚靚文宣圖！仲要有埋gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n12/12 &ldquo;United We Stand&rdquo; Rally: half-year commemoration of 12 June, the start of the anti-ELAB movement<br />\n- Retract the &ldquo;riots&rdquo; categorisation of all protests<br />\n- Drop all charges against arrested protestors<br />\n<br />\nDate: 12 December 2019 (Thursday)<br />\nTime: 19:00-21:00<br />\nVenue: Edinburgh Place<br />\nOrganiser: Hong Kong Civil Assembly Team #HKCATeam <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*Letter of No Objection issued</span><br />\n<br />\n#HongKong<br />\n#HongKongProtest<br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n#光復香港時代革命<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=15e0978b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/</a><br />\nInstagram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKCAT%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c7a9b084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/</a><br />\nTwitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=76cef0df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKCATeam</a><br />\n<br />\n另民間集會團隊現正發起眾籌<br />\n詳情：<br />\n[雪地插J求助] 頂左六個月，民間集會團隊實在頂唔住要眾籌，求大家捐少少<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776047</a><br />\n眾籌連結： <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=3f3a2acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">612 半週年</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">中大二橋之戰一個月</span></span><br />\n讓我地於12.12 呢個有多重意義嘅日子<br />\n再次聚首一堂<br />\n一齊齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"d917effd1e1a4db02a4c0095d944ee3555c9d6a2","tid":1778550,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ef34e347481d1ece4f688c3a1b2bbd7362c15f","tid":1778550,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1fafedf4b709572b9924a82e4db4721196d86a","tid":1778550,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7c1be9d081840bab34a4cd21813c48f56430c7","tid":1778550,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score